ards/ |title=The 2017 Detroit Film Critics Society Awards |publisher=[[Detroit Film Critics Society]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618075856/http://detroitfilmcritics.com/awards/ |archive-date=June 18, 2018 |access-date=July 24, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Dorian Awards]]\n| 2012\n| Film Performance of the Year\n| {{sort|Iron Lady|''[[The Iron Lady (film)|The Iron Lady]]''}}\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/race/modern-family-lgbt-michael-fassbender-meryl-streep-282452 |title=Gay and Lesbian Critics Name British Drama 'Weekend' Best Film of the Year |last=Kilday |first=Gregg |date=January 16, 2012 |website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117154504/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/race/modern-family-lgbt-michael-fassbender-meryl-streep-282452 |archive-date=November 17, 2015 |access-date=July 24, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2018\n| Timeless Star {{dagger|alt=Indicates non-competitive categories}}\n| {{sortname|Meryl|Streep|nolink=1}}\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/dorian-awards-call-me-by-your-name-named-film-year-1080560 |title=Dorian Awards: 'Call Me by Your Name' Hailed as Film of the Year |last=Kilday |first=Gregg |date=January 31, 2018 |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=January 31, 2018 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180131204827/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/dorian-awards-call-me-by-your-name-named-film-year-1080560 |archive-date=January 31, 2018 |df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"5\" | [[Drama Desk Award]]\n| 1976\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Actress in a Play|Outstanding Actress in a Play]]\n| ''Secret Service'', ''[[A Memory of Two Mondays]]'', ''[[List of one-act plays by Tennessee Williams#27 Wagons Full of Cotton|27 Wagons Full of Cotton]