s]]<br />[[Ingrid Burny]]<br />[[Rosine Roland]]||{{BEL}}||align=\"right\"| \n|}\n</div>\n{{Clr|left}}\n<br />\n{{clr}}\n\n=== C1 ===\n<div style=\"float:left;text-align:left;padding-right:5px\">\n{| style=\"border-style:solid;border-width:1px;border-color:#808080;background-color:#EFEFEF\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"2\" width=\"385px\"\n|+ style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 0.5em\"|Men\n|- bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n! Rank\n! Athlete\n! Country\n! Time\n|- bgcolor=\"#F7F6A8\"\n|align=center| {{Gold1}} ||[[Peter Sodomka]]||{{TCH}}||align=\"right\"| \n|- bgcolor=\"#DCE5E5\"\n|align=center| {{Silver2}} ||[[Bernd Heinemann]]||{{FRG}}||align=\"right\"| \n|- bgcolor=\"#FFDAB9\"\n|align=center| {{Bronze3}} ||[[Walter Gehlen]]||{{FRG}}||align=\"right\"| \n|}\n</div>\n<div style=\"float:right;text-align:left;padding-right:5px\">\n{| style=\"border-style:solid;border-width:1px;border-color:#808080;background-color:#EFEFEF\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"2\" width=\"385px\"\n|+ style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 0.5em\"|Men team\n|- bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n! Rank\n! Athlete\n! Country\n! Time \n|- bgcolor=\"#F7F6A8\" <br />\n|align=center| {{Gold1}} ||[[Walter Gehlen]]<br />[[Bernd Heinemann]]<br />[[Wolfgang Jogwer]]||{{FRG}}||align=\"right\"|\n|- bgcolor=\"#DCE5E5\"\n|align=center|{{Silver2}} ||[[Jiri Vocka]]<br />[[Karel Tresnak]]<br />[[Peter Sodomka]]||{{TCH}}||align=\"right\"| \n|- bgcolor=\"#FFDAB9\"\n|align=center| {{Bronze3}} ||[[John Sweet (canoer)|John Sweet]]<br />[[Al Button]]<br />[[Russ Nichols]]||{{USA}}||align=\"right\"| \n|}\n</div>\n{{Clr|left}}\n<br />\n{{clr}}\n\n=== C2 ===\n<div style=\"float:left;text-align:left;padding-right:5px\">\n{| style=\"border-style:solid;border-width:1px;border-color:#808080;background-color:#EFEFEF\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"2\" width=\"385px\"\n|+ style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 0.5em\"|Men\n|- bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n! Rank\n! Athlete\n! Country\